<br>
We've had a pair of wurmscale fistwraps drop and they went to a level 59 monk who already has his ST key.  We're coming up for NToV again on rotation and I'm hoping we'll get another drop, but they are kinda rare.  I'm considering holding off on them since we kill the Itraer often and maybe he'll drop a Fist of Acrylia for once in his miserable floating existence.  We don't get to THO often enough to hope for Horns of Chaos, altho those would be nice as well.  Hell, I'd even take a Fist of Lightning at this point.<br>
<br>
