<br>
If there are monks in your guild that are sorely hurting for DPS, I would suggest passing on it and letting them upgrade.  Wurmscale is a Very big DPS upgrade over epic/som/sos and most other combinations of pre-ntov weapons (excepting ST).<br>
<br>
Personally, I would skip the FoL and try to score a different haste item like Belt of the Destroyer or Earring of Speed if you're shooting for 41% haste since you're killing those mobs.<br>
<br>
If you get the FoL, you'll find you're spending alot more points.  IE, get FoL, then you drop a Luclin mob and want that Horn of Chaos or maybe GFoA or possibly even Fist of Nature off Tunare... except now you need to get another haste item and end up bagging the FoL... 8P<br>
<br>
LaotzuQigong<br>
